{"tid":1570284,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候加多句口號","createTime":"2019-09-15T04:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T04:09:38.000Z","uid":292536,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d7da807663f42adf0ef65fe2c4445682b4df8dce","tid":1570284,"uid":292536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:03:04.000Z","msg":"而家侵略香港嘅就係共產黨，要光復香港就自然需要反共。「驅逐共匪」或者「驅逐共黨」都係好嘅選擇（個人鍾意驅逐共匪）。加多呢一句喺「光復香港」前面係必須嘅，提醒我哋最終嘅目的係要經過踢走共產黨而達致效果。<br />\n<br />\n「揭竿起義」，話畀人聽呢個係一場要打返來嘅革命。「全民革命」，每一個香港人都責無旁貸，唔可以設身事外。如果你想「時代革命」嘅都得，但係有啲叔伯同我反映話有一種覺得好似唔關佢哋事嘅感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">驅逐共匪，光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">揭竿起義，全民革命</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇小一句口號嘅威力。名不正則言不順，言不順則事不成；要打破香港人對共產黨嘅恐懼就要由一句口號開始。依家嘅武力同參與程度樽頸位都係因為恐懼而限制我哋嘅能力，唔消滅恐懼就算拖林鄭上斷頭台你都唔夠膽斬落去。<br />\n<br />\n跟我講：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">驅逐共匪，光復香港</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民起義，時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n認同請幫手推"},{"pid":"d021ffbec133da006dd74e2ca2f6f9f8713c8b17","tid":1570284,"uid":292536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">驅逐共匪，光復香港</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民起義，時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"318d1e9f1623fa92679558476c104f02c900bf86","tid":1570284,"uid":182997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:05:20.000Z","msg":"驅逐共匪，光復香港<br />\n全民起義，時代革命"},{"pid":"71d18f2395a51214aa3b15d4a27d974b7f563f8b","tid":1570284,"uid":292536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:05:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">驅逐共匪，光復香港</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">揭竿起義，全民革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"56cf33a0221e8a1f4de62bf0862903d9863aeb4c","tid":1570284,"uid":292536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:07:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">驅逐共匪，光復香港<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">揭竿起義，全民革命<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"edecbac4906826da7e14ebca1833a3ea10c5191b","tid":1570284,"uid":292536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"318d1e9f1623fa92679558476c104f02c900bf86","tid":1570284,"uid":182997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:05:20.000Z","msg":"驅逐共匪，光復香港<br />\n全民起義，時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:09:38.000Z","msg":"嗌多幾次！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>驅逐共匪，光復香港</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>揭竿起義，全民革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>驅逐共匪，光復香港</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全民起義，時代革命</strong></span></span>"}]}